# Hyperscale-rs workflow

- **Links:** From `shared/hyperscale-flow-data.js` only. Use `data-crate`, `data-file`, `data-repo`; load `hyperscale-flow-data.js` + `hyperscale-links.js`. No hardcoded repo URLs in HTML.
- **After hyperscale-rs changes:** Run `node scripts/check-hyperscale-changes.js` (path in `scripts/hyperscale-repo.config.js`); re-check the modules it lists.
- **Tables:** Use `<div class="table-wrap">` and `<table class="flow-steps">`. Step column is narrow by default; if the first column has long text (e.g. stage names), add class `flow-steps-wide-first` to the table. See `shared/styles.css` for `.flow-steps` and `.content-table`.

Full workflow: **`shared/HYPERSCALE_FLOW_README.md`**.
